OL,3,CMum 'not going away' in search for
OL,4,Canswers over son's Cyprus death
OL,6,FA mother says she is "not going away"
OL,7,Fin her search for answers five years
OL,8,Fafter her son fell to his death from a
OL,9,Fbalcony in Northern Cyprus.
OL,11,FJordan Cook, 23, had been living and
OL,12,Fworking in the country for 18 months
OL,13,Fwhen he was found dead in 2021.
OL,15,FHis mother, Charlie Dobson, from
OL,16,FDoncaster, said Cypriot police
OL,17,Finitially ruled his death a suicide,
OL,18,Fbut later told her an investigation
OL,19,Fwas ongoing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1775675472
OL,3,CMum 'not going away' in search for
OL,4,Canswers over son's Cyprus death
OL,6,FFive years on, she said the country's
OL,7,Fauthorities had gone silent on the
OL,8,Fcase and approaches made by West
OL,9,FYorkshire Police on her behalf had
OL,10,Fbeen rebuffed.
OL,12,F"My thought is that (the Cypriot
OL,13,Fpolice) think I am just going to go
OL,14,Faway and carry on," Ms Dobson said.
OL,15,F"But they don't know me. I am a mother
OL,16,Fwho has lost her only child, and I am
OL,17,Fgoing to fight for justice regardless
OL,18,Fof what it takes.
OL,26,@tD@UpmuD@Gpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1775675472
OL,3,CMum 'not going away' in search for
OL,4,Canswers over son's Cyprus death
OL,6,F"Whatever consequences I face for
OL,7,Fbeing an outspoken British woman in
OL,8,FNorthern Cyprus, I am prepared to take
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,F"I am not going to go away."
OL,13,FMs Dobson said there were no "red
OL,14,Fflags" about her son's behaviour
OL,15,Fsuggesting he was suicidal in the days
OL,16,Fbefore his death.
OL,18,F"I spoke to him the day before," she
OL,19,Fsaid. "He was looking at Airbnbs and
OL,20,Fhotels, as it would have been his
OL,21,Fbirthday two weeks later."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1775675472
OL,3,CMum 'not going away' in search for
OL,4,Canswers over son's Cyprus death
OL,6,FA coroner in Wakefield gave an open
OL,7,Fverdict at his inquest.
OL,9,FMs Dobson said she was told she would
OL,10,Fhave to recruit a Cypriot lawyer to
OL,11,Faccess official documents about her
OL,12,Fson's death, at a cost of #10,000.
OL,14,FShe has already downsized her home and
OL,15,Fspent savings to finance her efforts.
OL,17,FShe said: "It's frustrating. It's
OL,18,Fpreventing me from grieving and to
OL,19,Faccept things. I'm still struggling
OL,20,Fwith accepting that Jordan's not
OL,21,Fcoming back.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1775675472
OL,3,CMum 'not going away' in search for
OL,4,Canswers over son's Cyprus death
OL,6,F"I don't have closure, I don't have
OL,7,Fthe answers."
OL,9,FMs Dobson's MP Sally Jameson is
OL,10,Fsupporting her campaign.
OL,12,FShe said: "It's so important that when
OL,13,Fsomething like this happens, people
OL,14,Fget the answers, but also that they
OL,15,Fget the justice.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1775675472
OL,3,CMum 'not going away' in search for
OL,4,Canswers over son's Cyprus death
OL,6,F"She's highlighted a number of
OL,7,Ffailings that have happened throughout
OL,8,Fthe system, and I think it's important
OL,9,Fthat we make sure as a government that
OL,10,Fsomething like this doesn't happen
OL,11,Fagain."
OL,13,FChris Christofi, a lawyer specialising
OL,14,Fin Cypriot law, said the local
OL,15,Fpolitics of the area complicated
OL,16,Fattempts to gain answers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
