PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1775675472
OL,3,CMum 'not going away' in search for
OL,4,Canswers over son's Cyprus death
OL,6,FHe said: "Unfortunately, we're not
OL,7,Ftalking about the Republic of Cyprus,
OL,8,Fwe're talking about the Turkish
OL,9,FRepublic of Northern Cyprus, an
OL,10,Fillegal state - it's not recognised by
OL,11,Fanyone other than Turkey.
OL,13,F"And your ability to pursue a remedy
OL,14,Fin that area is very difficult and
OL,15,Fvery much fashioned by the local
OL,16,Fpolitics and by local economy and and
OL,17,Fultimately by Turkey itself."
OL,19,FA Foreign Office spokesperson
OL,20,Fconfirmed it was supporting Ms
OL,21,FDobson's case.
OL,26,@nD@JOU
